&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;This is a tutorial about how to connect Proteus with Arduino IDE by serial port. Take BCD Adder for an instance.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
